data.description: This fantastic 2 bedroom, 1 bath home is set on a massive DOUBLE LOT in the centrally located Four Corners area of 29 Palms. You'll be blown away by the amazing views as you approach the property from paved Mesquite Springs Road, and love that the home is nestled at the base of a scenic hillside. You'll also appreciate that two sides of the home are surrounded by open desert, while a third is spaced well away from the nearest home by two undeveloped lots, accentuating the amazing views. A detached 1 car garage features extra storage space, while the circular drive offers ample additional space for vehicles. The covered front entryway beckons you to enter via the inviting screened in porch, which provides a fantastic place to kick back and enjoy the serenity of this property. Step inside the home to find yourself in a nicely sized living room with carpeting, mini-splits for perfect climate control, and lots of windows to bring the views inside (fireplace is not currently functional). The kitchen has been nicely remodeled with lots of cabinetry for storage, a gas range for the serious chef, and laminate flooring. The bathroom has also been updated with the latest finishes, and includes a fully tiled walk-in shower. The first bedroom features its own access to the bathroom, and is generously sized and well lit with both a walk-in closet and a regular closet for tons of storage. A stylish sliding barn door brings you into the second bedroom, which enjoys laminate floors that match the kitchen and lots of cheerful windows. Stepping outside, you'll find a wonderful back sitting area with incredible views and a sunken patio, and also note the convenient outdoor laundry room. There is also plenty of backyard living space to spread out in and enjoy, including a fire pit! Covering practical matters, you'll be pleased to know the seller states that the electrical panel was also updated a couple of years ago. This sale includes two lots; the home's lot of .386 acres and the garage's lot of .4242 acres (APN 0617-011-08-0000) for total of .8102 acres. Did we mention that it's just minutes from the Joshua Tree National Park entrance? Incredible! Book a showing to see this great property for yourself.
